:''Surrender or you'll die''
:''For we are''
:''The Brigton Derry Boys''<ref>{{cite web|author= |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/uk/359039.stm |title=The bitter divide|publisher=BBC |date= |accessdate=2014-05-03}}</ref>

An alternative Rangers specific version was later written.<ref name=gg />

:''Hello, Hello''
:''We are the Rangers Boys''
:''Hello, Hello''
:''You'll know us by our noise''
:''We'll give anything to see our team''
:''At Ibrox or away''
:''For we are''
:''The Glasgow Rangers Boys''

